// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1139 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6a019516-2575-5028-8800-d04f26085318

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
